            <div class="xg4goql xg4goqa" data-testimonial="quotes">
             <p class="xg4goqm"><span>“We often look at our Fastly logs before we look at our origin’s logs. Once, we did a release, and it turned out that there was an edge case throwing tons of service errors. We looked up at our big Fastly Dashboard in the office and noticed that the pattern of errors had radically altered. By visualizing Fastly’s logs, we are able to identify and quickly fix bugs.”</span></p>
             <div>
              <p class="xg4goqn">Ross Paul</p>
              <p class="xg4goqo">CTO</p>
