       <div class="tabs"> 
        <div class="cmp-tabs vspacebtncomp-top" data-cmp-is="tabs"> 
         <ol role="tablist" class="cmp-tabs__tablist" aria-multiselectable="false"> 
          <li role="tab" class="cmp-tabs__tab cmp-tabs__tab--active" tabindex="0" data-cmp-hook-tabs="tab">IBM</li> 
          <li role="tab" class="cmp-tabs__tab " tabindex="-1" data-cmp-hook-tabs="tab">CLOUDFLARE</li> 
         </ol> 
         <div role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" class="cmp-tabs__tabpanel cmp-tabs__tabpanel--active" data-cmp-hook-tabs="tabpanel">
          <div class="customer-carousel"> 
           <div class="grid-12 vspacebtncomp"> 
            <div class="img-container img-container--right"> 
             <div class="revealAnimation"> 
              <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/images/homepage/homepage-IBM.png" alt="IBM"> 
             </div> 
            </div> 
            <div class="icon-container icon-container--left"> 
             <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/images/homepage/IBM-logo-2.png" alt="IBM Logo - Partners"> 
            </div> 
            <div class="descriptionBox descriptionBox--left" style="background-color:#0174c3;"> 
             <div class="description"> 
              <p><span style="">"Now with this very business-friendly solution, we no longer need to expose those technical aspects to the end-user."&nbsp;</span><br> </p> 
              <h6>WEBER YUAN, LEAD ARCHITECT, CIO IDENTITY SERVICES, IBM&nbsp;</h6> 
              <div class="btn-container vertical" style="background-color:#0174c3;"> <a href="/content/dam/digicert/videos/digicert_ibm_181016_720p.mp4" class="btn video white" target="_blank" style="margin-right:px;
				 		   margin-bottom:px;"> View Video</a> 
              </div> 
             </div> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" class="cmp-tabs__tabpanel" data-cmp-hook-tabs="tabpanel">
          <div class="customer-carousel"> 
           <div class="grid-12 vspacebtncomp"> 
            <div class="img-container img-container--right"> 
             <div class="revealAnimation"> 
              <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/en/images/about/partners/Cloudflare.png" alt="Cloudflare - Partners"> 
             </div> 
            </div> 
            <div class="icon-container icon-container--left"> 
             <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/images/homepage/homepage-03.png" alt="Cloudflare Logo - Partners"> 
            </div> 
            <div class="descriptionBox descriptionBox--left" style="background-color:#0174c3;"> 
             <div class="description"> 
              <p>“DigiCert, to me, feels like—which is unique in the industry—a professionally run software development organization. Not just a vendor. It's a development organization."</p> 
              <h6>PATRICK DONAHUE, DIRECTOR OF PRODUCT MANAGEMENT</h6> 
